These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, rose, aconite
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, hot-chocolate, coffee
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, pall-mall, fonseca, baccarat
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, scooter, motorbike, trike
City: liverpool, edinburgh, london, miami
 1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person driving the bike is the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the fonseca-smoker is the person who growsdahlia##1
10. the person traveling to london is the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower          | zinnia    | rose      | dahlia  | aconite     |
| Beverage         | coffee    | hot-chocolate   | lemonade | sprite      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall       | havana | fonseca     | baccarat    |
| Transport   | trike | scooter         | bike  | motorbike    |
| City           | london      | miami       | liverpool | edinburgh |

