.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
House: victorian, art-deco, cottage, townhouse
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, go, backgammon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, vegafina, cain, fonseca
City: edinburgh, paris, hamburg, boston
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, potato, radish, cabbage
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
 5. the victorian house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 6. the person eating radish is on the right of the cottage house##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is the fonseca-smoker##1
 9. the person playing go is the cain-smoker##1
10. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the cottage house is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| House      | art-deco      | victorian     | cottage    | townhouse |
| Game   | mah-jongg | canasta   | go   | backgammon           |
| Cigar   | vegafina  | fonseca     | cain    | davidoff         |
| City           | boston         | paris | hamburg     | edinburgh        |
| Food         | cranberry     | cabbage  | potato | radish       |

