.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, marigold, iris, lily
House: ranch-style, craftsman, cottage, art-deco
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, action, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, country, house, disco
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, july, may
 1. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person who growsiris is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the fan of house is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsiris##1
 7. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the art-deco house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
12. the person who growsiris is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Flower          | daisy    | lily      | iris  | marigold   |
| House   | art-deco     | cottage      | craftsman | ranch-style      |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts       | crime         | family  | action         |
| Music-Genre         | folk | country | house  | disco |
| Birthday     | july       | october         | may   | march        |

