.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, march, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, siglo, bongani
House: cottage, ranch-style, gothic-revival, cape-cod
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, sudoku, cooking
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, teacher, accountant, fisherman
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the teacher##1
 3. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 5. the librarian is on the far left##1
 6. the accountant is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
 8. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
12. the fisherman is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday      | march   | january   | august      | may     |
| Cigar          | siglo     | bluemaster   | bongani | game |
| House   | ranch-style | gothic-revival | cottage   | cape-cod       |
| Hobby           | drawing       | board-games      | cooking     | sudoku |
| Job     | librarian    | accountant     | fisherman     | teacher     |

