.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, onion, peas
City: rome, boston, prague, hamburg
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, apricot, green, chestnut
House: gothic-revival, tower, wooden, colonial
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, drama, scientific, sports
 1. the wooden house is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is the person who likes mauve##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the tower house##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the person eating apple is the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person eating peas is the tower house##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person eating onion is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Food    | apple     | cauliflower  | peas       | onion      |
| City       | prague    | hamburg        | rome  | boston      |
| Color         | apricot  | chestnut | mauve | green |
| House         | gothic-revival | colonial          | tower         | wooden      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | family     | scientific       | sports          |

