.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, taxi, car
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, begonia, marigold
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, architect, videographer, bartender
City: colone, hamburg, marseilles, san-francisco
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, september, october, april
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is the bartender##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is the person driving the car##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the architect##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is the videographer##1
10. the videographer is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Transport      | car       | taxi      | helicopter      | jet-ski    |
| Flower         | marigold | begonia | sunflower | poppy  |
| Job   | videographer    | architect     | bartender      | software-developer |
| City   | marseilles  | san-francisco     | colone    | hamburg  |
| Birthday           | september  | april       | december          | october      |

