.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, russian, spanish, brazilian
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, lavender, fuchsia, chestnut
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, security-guard, videographer, coach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, january, may
4 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, fish, horse
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
 2. the brazilian is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 3. the owner of the fish is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the videographer is on the right of the freelancer##1
 5. the freelancer is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the coach is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the american##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the american##1
 9. the security-guard is on the right of the russian##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the spanish##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the brazilian##1
12. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
13. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality          | brazilian      | russian     | american        | spanish     |
| Color         | fuchsia     | lilac    | chestnut | lavender |
| Job   | freelancer | videographer  | security-guard      | coach       |
| Birthday         | january      | august | february     | may        |
| Pet     | fish   | horse     | cat  | rabbit       |

