.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
City: hannover, marseilles, hamburg, london
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, nigerian, indian, chinese
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, orchid, rose
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, ivory, purple, hannover
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg
 1. the person who growsrose is the mexican##1
 2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the indian##1
 4. the nigerian is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the person who likes purple is the chinese##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the nigerian##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
10. the person traveling to london is the person who likes hannover##1
11. the person who likes hannover is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
12. the person who likes hannover is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| City        | marseilles    | london        | hannover        | hamburg      |
| Nationality       | indian       | mexican       | nigerian      | chinese |
| Flower         | tulip | rose | orchid | zinnia      |
| Color         | azure          | hannover         | ivory           | purple    |
| Game   | monopoly         | backgammon       | mah-jongg     | scrabble   |

 